      <section>
        <h3 class="feature-more-heading -deploy">Deploy new changes like a pro</h3>
        <p class="feature-more-summary">Trigger a new deployment from the terminal with one command or every time you push changes to a designated branch of your GitHub repository.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h3 class="feature-more-heading -control">SSL certificates out of the box</h3>
        <p class="feature-more-summary">WeDeploy Hosting automatically provisions a unique URL for every deployed service and configures SSL certificates for all services and custom domains.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
